sentences: He was elected as a Young Steinway Artist in 2011.

Wan has broadcast extensively on radio networks such as RTHK and other overseas services, and has given many highly acclaimed recitals throughout Europe and Asia including the Czech Republic, Germany, Hong Kong, Hungary, Italy, Spain, United Kingdom and a recital in Poland to mark the 200th anniversary of Frédéric Chopin's birth in 2010.

He made his Germany recital debut in 2007 and was praised by the German newspaper Der Odenwalder Zeitung as having "A very high musical sensibility" and as "an artist who inspires his audiences in his music".

In 2014, Blanc Wan will serve on the juries of Asia Piano Open Competition, Hong Kong International Piano Open Competition – The Liszt Award, as well as Macau Open Competition for Young Pianists, etc.
